suncertify.db
Class Record

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.db.Record

public class Record
extends java.lang.Object

The Record object is a representation of a record of the database. This class can be parameterized to work with multiple database's, making it abstract to the actual data it stores.

Version:
1.5
Author:
Pedro Oliveira
